data.name: Label10.Text
data.value: By registering an account in the Pamantasan ng Lungsod ng Pasig (PLP) Internship Management System, you agree to the following terms: 1. You are an authorized faculty member permitted to access and manage internship records. 2. All information provided must be accurate and truthful. 3. You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of all student and company data 4. Evaluations and visit logs must be submitted honestly and in accordance with PLP policies. 5. Any unauthorized access, data sharing, or misuse of the system is strictly prohibited. 6. PLP reserves the right to review, suspend, or deactivate accounts that violate these terms. By clicking "Sign Up", you confirm that you have read, understood, and agreed to these Terms and Conditions.
